name: Anchor Safes
overview: Are you looking for commercial or private use safes to keep your documents and valuable safe? Anchor Safes are the premium supplier of the best and most affordable electronic and standard safe products in Australia. Anchor Safe provides a range of over 250 safes including: In-Wall safes In-Floor safes Data & Media Protection safes Commercial & Office safes Fire & Theft-Resistant safes Cash Deposit safes Firearm safes Pharmacy & Drug safes SCEC & Government Approved Safes & Filing Cabinets Travel Agent IATA Approved safes Discounted delivery and installation of all commercial and personal safes
